# Plugin Architecture

The MD Import Force plugin follows an object-oriented architecture with several key components:

## Initialization Flow

1. Main plugin file: [md-import-force.php](mdc:md-import-force.php)
2. Plugin initializer: [class-md-import-force-initializer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-initializer.php)

## Core Components

### Handlers
- AJAX Handler: [class-md-import-force-ajax-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-ajax-handler.php)
- Media Handler: [class-md-import-force-media-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-media-handler.php)
- URL Handler: [class-md-import-force-url-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-url-handler.php)
- Error Handler: [class-md-import-force-error-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-error-handler.php)

### Importers
- Post Importer: [class-md-import-force-post-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-post-importer.php)
- Taxonomy Importer: [class-md-import-force-taxonomy-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-taxonomy-importer.php)
- Comment Importer: [class-md-import-force-comment-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-comment-importer.php)

### Utility Classes
- File Manager: [class-md-import-force-file-manager.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-file-manager.php)
- Logger: [class-md-import-force-logger.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-logger.php)
- Progress Tracker: [class-md-import-force-progress-tracker.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-progress-tracker.php)

### Management Classes
- Import Manager: [class-md-import-force-import-manager.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-import-manager.php)
